&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Design and manage a dynamic, complex schedule that reflects the CEO’s highest priorities and Acumen’s broader organizational needs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exercise excellent judgment in evaluating requests, identifying trade-offs, and sequencing commitments thoughtfully across competing demands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the CEO is fully prepared for every engagement, with clear and concise context on the who, what, where, why, and how.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and execute a seamless daily schedule, managing multiple simultaneous requests across time zones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage high-volume communications

