&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The Institutional Partnerships Senior Associate will support the advancement of Acumen’s institutional fundraising and partner engagement efforts in support of Acumen’s latest poverty and climate investment strategy and Acumen Academy. This role will focus on research, proposal development, partner communications, and coordination across teams. This is an excellent opportunity for someone interested in climate finance, impact investing, and institutional fundraising to gain hands-on experience working across global teams and external partners.&lt;/p&gt;
