&lt;li&gt;Prepare and present investment documentation for Acumen India’s Investment Committee&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the closing of transactions including negotiations of investment conditions (i.e., price, shareholders rights) along with the investees and Acumen legal team&lt;/li&gt;
