&lt;h1 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Short Term Analyst, Latin America, Acumen Academy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bogotá, Colombia&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Puedes leer la descripción del cargo en español &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/12s8OqbZ3gPycdW4AhnKvjFwTLJFJe1YkK1r4VdEAewc/edit?usp=sharing&quot;&gt;acá&lt;/a&gt;. Por favor envía tu hoja de vida en inglés.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please send CVs in English as it is required for the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Acumen Academy in Colombia is seeking a Short Term Analyst to strengthen our Spanish-language online learning ecosystem by supporting course operations, content creation, and learner engagement. The role offers the opportunity to work at the intersection of data, technology, education, and social impact—helping us deliver high-quality, accessible learning experiences for social innovators across Latin America. The Short Term Analyst will support backend operations for WhatsApp-based courses, analyze data to improve impact, and nurture a growing community of learners. This is an 8 month contract, ideally starting October 2026.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Acumen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Acumen is changing the way the world tackles poverty by investing in companies, leaders and ideas. We invest patient capital in businesses whose products and services are enabling the poor to transform their lives. To date, Acumen has positively impacted more than 500 million lives by investing $164M in 167 innovative, early-stage companies in Africa, Latin America, South Asia, and the United States. But investment isn’t only about capital–we’ve been investing in innovators for years, connecting with emerging leaders around the world and engaging them in collective dialogue, moral inquiry, and skill building.&lt;/p&gt;
